            <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E7%BA%A620%25%E6%88%90%E4%BA%BA%E6%85%A2%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%BF%E7%A7%98%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%88%91%E5%9B%BD%E7%BA%A620%25%E6%88%90%E4%BA%BA%E6%85%A2%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%BF%E7%A7%98%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#我国约20%成人慢性便秘#</span></a> <span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>阿卫健康上厕所建议：“掐点”拉，专心拉<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>早上起床的起立反射可以促进大肠蠕动，产生“屎意”。所以早上起床后是大肠活动最活跃的时间（男性排便一般在上午7~8时之间，女性晚1小时左右）。吃东西也容易让人有“屎意”。所以，推荐在起床后或餐后2小时内尝试排便。拉粑粑时要集中注意力，不要玩手机或读书，建议每次上厕所时间不超过10 分钟。那么问题来了，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%BD%A0%E6%AF%8F%E6%AC%A1%E4%B8%8A%E5%8E%95%E5%A4%A7%E6%A6%82%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E5%A4%9A%E4%B9%85%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%BD%A0%E6%AF%8F%E6%AC%A1%E4%B8%8A%E5%8E%95%E5%A4%A7%E6%A6%82%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E5%A4%9A%E4%B9%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#你每次上厕大概需要多久#</span></a>？<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%8A%E5%8E%95%E6%89%80%E9%80%94%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%83%E4%B8%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%86%B2%E5%8E%95%E6%89%80%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%8A%E5%8E%95%E6%89%80%E9%80%94%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%83%E4%B8%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%86%B2%E5%8E%95%E6%89%80%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#上厕所途中千万不要冲厕所#</span></a> <a href="http://t.cn/A6p2rXks" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
